USING: accessors models kernel ;
IN: models.arrow

TUPLE: arrow < model model quot ;

: <arrow> ( model quot -- arrow )
    f arrow new-model
        swap >>quot
        over >>model
        [ add-dependency ] keep ;

M: arrow model-changed
    [ [ value>> ] [ quot>> ] bi* call( old -- new ) ] [ nip ] 2bi
    set-model ;

M: arrow model-activated [ model>> ] keep model-changed ;
